    "description": "<div>\n<p style=\"margin: 20px 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 1.25em;\"><strong>The Slayer</strong> is a monster hunter, plain and simple. They&rsquo;re fast and lethal, equally at home confronting a horde of beasts and a single towering colossus. <br><em> Play the Slayer if you want to be right in the centre of every melee, flinging yourself into combat safe in the knowledge it'll hurt them more than it'll hurt you. </em></p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"font-size: 0.95em;\"><em> <strong>Instructions:</strong> You can drag-and-drop into your character sheet any <span style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary); border-radius: 2px; display: inline-block; padding: 1px 4px; font-style: normal;\"> <img style=\"border: none; color: var(--color-text-dark-inactive); height: 14px; margin: 2px 0 -2px; width: 14px;\" src=\"modules/pbta-rhapsodyofblood/assets/playbooks/suitcase.svg\" alt=\"\"> Item</span> you choose and it will automatically be assigned to its correct place. Everything else needs to be copy-pasted or input manually (this includes the background &amp; details and your stats). </em></p>\n<hr>\n<section class=\"grid grid-2col\">\n<div class=\"background\" style=\"border-right: dashed 1px black; padding-right: 10px;\">\n<h2 style=\"margin: 15px 0 10px;\">MAKING YOUR SLAYER</h2>\n<h3 style=\"border: none;\">Stats</h3>\nYou start with this array; add 1 to a stat of your choice.\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Iron</strong> +1</li>\n<li><strong>Glass</strong> &plusmn;0</li>\n<li><strong>Sulphur</strong> &plusmn;0</li>\n<li><strong>Mercury</strong> -1</li>\n<li><em>Blood starts at 0.</em></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 style=\"border: none;\">Looks</h3>\n<p>Maimed body, lithe body, muscular body, stout body <br>Asian, South Asian, Black, Caucasian, Hispanic, Latino, Indigenous, Middle Eastern</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 style=\"border: none;\">Names</h3>\n<p>Lilianna, Isidor, Ayako, Farhana, Laura, Peter, Simon, Julian, Laurens, Jiddu</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 style=\"border: none;\">Gear</h3>\n<p>Make a weapon (1 perk, 1 flaw).</p>\n<hr style=\"border: 1px solid #3f3c2f;\">\n<div class=\"flexrow\">\n<div>\n<h4>Pick one extra armament:</h4>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.gear.Item.7CPY6k9AQUzys9qz]{A pistol}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.gear.Item.rIJeIiPuQ6jbR7iJ]{Breastplate or mail shirt}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.gear.Item.96fCnM3u1ZbTaK0f]{A shield}</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h4>Pick two pieces of utility gear:</h4>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.gear.Item.qHcFCXCHKC7gLo5K]{Torches and fire lighting kit}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.gear.Item.gmJsuhRA9VM0wKr4]{Bandages and healing salves}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.gear.Item.Jxuzi4D0KbwUdUEL]{Anti-venoms and stimulants}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.gear.Item.2fU8JamvFJY5t7wQ]{As many rations as you need}</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h3 style=\"border: none;\">Covenants</h3>\n<p>Go around the table, introducing your explorer to the group. Pick a covenant you have with the player to your left at rank 1. Examples:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You&rsquo;re teaching them to fight.</li>\n<li>They nursed you back to health.</li>\n<li>You&rsquo;re monster-hunter partners</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Add extra details and context for the covenant the player to your right has chosen.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"moves\">\n<h2 style=\"margin: 15px 0 10px;\">Moves</h2>\n<h3 style=\"border: none;\">Bonded Moves</h3>\n<p>Pick two:</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.moves.Item.kmBiBIzfU1opG1z4]{Blood Trail}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.moves.Item.ORRYjOxJQZUUfc5z]{Lightning Swift}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.moves.Item.wuyScclkbXVoKdYP]{Regain Momentum}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.moves.Item.eX9Rx7KyRiyztRiZ]{Trick Weapon}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.moves.Item.PVwD10sw8lW9QvwU]{Trophy}</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 style=\"border: none;\">Death Move</h3>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.moves.Item.wpPLbqJoG2Th9U24]{Death Move [The Slayer]}</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 style=\"border: none;\">Blood Gifts</h3>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.moves.Item.j32AumqwfKPFc0t6]{Burning Blood}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.moves.Item.wFQK3fgXPpKCg9yr]{Frenzy}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.moves.Item.61hpzKzTlAng1ge2]{Lupine}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pbta-rhapsodyofblood.moves.Item.SyhWlskhGjdZObBp]{Voice of Command}</p>\n</div>\n</section>",
